project: Welcome, casual, to the tutorial. I'm here to school you on how to play vidja gaymes. You are playing as Bob, the little purple square dude.
Bottom Text Venezuela Iphone CXV 1 Billion Dead Vine "Boom" Sound

You can use the A & D keys to make Bob walk left and right, and the arrow keys to do the same with Dave. Though if you didn't know how the WASD keys worked, I'd question how you're still breathing without a brain.
Press the W key or the up arrow in order to jump. Again, baby stuff. You know all of this already. Let's move on.
You can use springs such as this in order to reach greater heights.
You can fall through black platforms such as this by pressing S or Down arrow. Easy stuff.

^ This is a Power Up. There are more kinds, but as of right now the Grow Arrow is the only one that concerns you. It makes you much bigger and much more dense for 15 seconds, letting you hit the ball harder and move physics objects easier. Use it to destroy that wall.
Watch out for lava. If you fall in it, you have to restart the level. Bob is too poor to afford a healthbar.
Cash is the goal. Get into it to complete the level and move on to the next.

This young man's name is Bob, and he wakes to the sound of the landlord pounding on his door. Apparently he fell into a coma six months caused by drinking too much gasoline. Figures. 
Anyways, Bob's landlord, Dave, tells him he needs to get rent money or else Bob will be sleeping for a VERY long time. Luckily, Bob knows where to get some cash...

Nice job finding this place. Here's the lowdown: basically every level will have a secret spot with a small upgrade in it. This upgrade will stick with you for the rest of the game, and if you can manage to find all of them, there might be something special for you...
This upgrade is pretty simple: it makes powerups last a bit longer, and it gives an upgrade to something you'll find later.
Press space while holding the WASD keys to dash in the direction you are holding the keys. This consumes some of your gas, so use it wisely.
Clicking when Bob has filled up on gas will shoot a fireball towards where he clicks. These have a few uses, one of which is the ability to push buttons they hit.
To reach your final foe and claim the remainder of his cash, you must ascend the TOWER OF DOOM.
